subNode:value.scalar:string: Display the website(s) your visitors came from.
Here we break down the 10 most popular referral websites that call customers to your e-store.
When visiting a webpage, the referrer is the URL of the previous webpage from which a link was followed.
A referrer enables you to know which keywords visitors use in search engines when browsing for your online store.
Someone who posts a link to your shop.
A partner who has agreed to a link exchange in order to attract new customers.
